	* date if format is:
		* dd MMM YYY - hh:mm
		* dd-MMM-YY or dd-MM-YYYY (can be / or space in place of -)
		* MMM is Jan, Feb, etc
	* number is digits, with optional decimal point
	* otherwise treated as text
